Simple uart driver, polling.

Makeflags:
  CONFIG_UART_GPIO_TX_PULL_NONE
    Hint to driver: do not place a gpio pull-up on TX
  CONFIG_UART_GPIO_RX_PULL_UP
    Hint to driver: place a gpio pull-up on RX
  CONFIG_UART_GPIO_RTS_PULL_NONE
    Hint to driver: do not place a gpio pull-up on RTS
  CONFIG_UART_GPIO_CTS_PULL_UP
    Hint to driver: place a gpio pull-up on CTS
